bma - Bike Mileage Add

USAGE:
    bma <date> <index> <bike> <distance> [tags]

DESCRIPTION:
    Add a bike ride record to the mileage log. Automatically converts
    distance from miles to kilometers. If the record already exists
    (Date, Index, Bike), an error is returned.

ARGUMENTS:
    date
        Date of ride (format: YYYY/MM/DD)

    index
        Ride number for the day (1, 2, 3...)

    bike
        Name of the bike

    distance
        Distance in km, recorded to repository in miles to be compatible with historical data (future releases may change this)

    tags
        Optional tags for the ride

EXAMPLES:
    bma 2025/03/25 1 road-bike 15.2 "commute"
    bma 2025/03/25 2 mountain-bike 8.7 "trail"
    bma 2025/03/26 1 road-bike 12.1